  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Chalet Faure is on a half board basis. Drinks are not included</p>
<p>Each morning you can enjoy a continental breakfast buffet including fresh fruit, cereal, meats and cheeses, breads and pastries, along with juices and hot drinks</p>
<p>Evening meals can be taken in a range of local restaurants including the downstairs wine bar il Lampione, Farola serving tasty tapas dishes or Assietta dishing up tasty  meals from the Piemonte region. Farola is just a minutes' walk from the hotel, and Assietta is about a three minutes' walk</p>]]></cateringDescription>
